                <h2>Purpose</h2>
                <p>This website aggregates questions asked in interviews for the biggest companies and displays them in
                    an intuitive
                    and easily readable manner. The goal is to serve as a quick study guide for people trying to
                    minimize the amount
                    of time they have to spend on interview prep. Existing interview question sites like Glassdoor are
                    bloated and
                    slow, making it unnecessarily difficult to retrieve the most relevant information when it comes to
                    interview
                    questions.
                </p>
            </section>
