            <section>
                <h2>Functionality</h2>
                <h3>Core Features:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li><b>Landing Page:</b> Explains the purpose and functionality of the website.</li>
                    <li><b>Company Overview:</b> Provides an overview of a company along with a simple visual or table
                        displaying the average difficulty of the interview questions asked by the company.</li>
                    <li><b>Interview Question Section:</b> Lists out the interview questions for a company in a
                        paginated section along with the most important fields (question, answer, date submitted,
                        position, etc). Filters allow for the list of questions to be narrowed down (filter by
                        complexity, job title/family, etc).</li>
                    <li><b>User Profiles:</b> Created when users create an account. An account allows users to submit,
                        rate, and report interview questions.</li>
                    <li><b>Detailed Question Page:</b> Shows all of the detailed information for the interview question
                        and also allows for the submission and display of user comments for the question.
                    <li><b>Question Form:</b> Allows users to add an interview question for a company.</li>
                    <li><b>AI-Generated Solutions:</b> OpenAI or Google integration to add AI-generated answers to
                        user-submitted questions.</li>
                    <li><b>Reporting Function:</b> Allow users to report questions that they think are inappropriate,
                        irrelevant, etc. A message will let users know that they have successfully reported a question,
                        and there will be a system on the backend to flag these questions for manual review.</li>
                    <li><b>Statistics Page:</b> Shows more detailed statistics on the breakdown of questions for each
                        company, including things like total number of questions, interview locations, years of
                        experience, etc.
                    </li>
                </ol>
                <br>
                <h3>Extra Features <i>(optional extra credit):</i></h3>
                <ol>
                    <li><b>Upvoting Function:</b> Allow users to upvote questions that also came up for them or are
                        insightful. Total upvotes can be displayed for each question and questions can also be sorted by
                        upvotes.
                    </li>
                    <li><b>User Profile Customization:</b> Allow users to customize their profile page with things like
                        custom avatars, bios, and contact information.</li>
                    <li><b>Schedule Live Mock Interviews:</b> Allows users to schedule a live mock interview with a
                        professional interviewer.</li>
                </ol>
            </section>
